{"tid":2303617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社署即日起接受確診者5,000元津貼申請","createTime":"2020-11-28T06:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T06:25:20.000Z","uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd27a5f5d0cc1c37cea21999de6673237ec37cc","tid":2303617,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"社會福利署昨日宣佈，由即日起接受確診武漢肺炎的合資格香港居民申請一筆過5,000元恩恤現金津貼，申請人須符合兩項資格，第一是獲衞生署確認在11月22日或以後在本地感染武漢肺炎的香港居民，第二是現時受僱但不享有有薪病假或自僱人士，並因須在公立醫院留院治療而面對經濟困難。<br />\n<br />\n社署指，市民無須接受特定的經濟審查，但必須聲明他們符合上述資格並就其目前的就業狀況提供基本資料，並可由今日起向其接受治療的醫院的醫務社工提出申請，市民亦可自行提出申請，如有需要可委任一位家人、親屬或代理人代為處理申請。如申請人未能在接受治療期間完成申請，亦可在康復出院後盡快遞交申請。"},{"pid":"292615f0b0fd0b54ccbce7770df55dce69f1aa82","tid":2303617,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"的確係失業人士嘅救贖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重覆中有冇重複拎"},{"pid":"896ea4831c5652f8ef4a188b49d87cf2b29622a1","tid":2303617,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYjRubM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYjRubM.gif&h=5ae0e398&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb243b64b5dc6de7bc8b54d277e3acfde3b95a04","tid":2303617,"uid":41154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"896ea4831c5652f8ef4a188b49d87cf2b29622a1","tid":2303617,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYjRubM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYjRubM.gif&h=5ae0e398&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk